==English==

===Transitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|dereferenc|e}}

# {{complang}} To dereference a memory location is to obtain the value stored therein, in an execution context which interprets the value obtained as the [[address]] of a memory location; thus in the context of computer languages which support [[pointer|pointers]], to '''dereference''' a pointer is to access the thing to which it points.

